Minishell Parsing Cases

command [options] [arguments] [< input_file] [> output_file] [>> append_file] [&] [| command2 [options] [arguments] [< input_file] [> output_file] [>> append_file] [&]]

1. Simple Commands
   - Input: ls
   - Output: Command: ls, Arguments: []

2. Command with Arguments
   - Input: grep "text" file.txt
   - Output: Command: grep, Arguments: ["text", "file.txt"]

3. Pipes
   - Input: ls | grep "text"
   - Output: Pipes: [("ls", []), ("grep", ["text"])]

4. Redirection (Input)
   - Input: grep "text" < file.txt
   - Output: Command: grep, Arguments: ["text"], Input Redirection: file.txt

5. Redirection (Output)
   - Input: ls > output.txt
   - Output: Command: ls, Arguments: [], Output Redirection: output.txt

6. Appending Output
   - Input: echo "text" >> file.txt
   - Output: Command: echo, Arguments: ["text"], Append Output: file.txt

7. Background Execution
   - Input: sleep 10 &
   - Output: Command: sleep, Arguments: ["10"], Background: true

8. Quotes
   - Input: echo "Hello World"''
   - Output: Command: echo, Arguments: ["Hello World"]

9. Escaped Characters
   - Input: echo \"Hello\\ World\"
   - Output: Command: echo, Arguments: ["Hello\\ World"]

10. Command Substitution
    - Input: echo $(ls)
    - Output: Command: echo, Arguments: [$(ls)]

11. Complex Pipelines
    - Input: cat file.txt | grep "text" | sort
    - Output: Pipes: [("cat", ["file.txt"]), ("grep", ["text"]), ("sort", [])]

12. Error Cases
    - Input: ls | | grep "text"
    - Output: Error: Invalid syntax near '|'

13. Empty Command
    - Input: 
    - Output: Error: No command entered

14. Invalid Redirection
    - Input: ls >
    - Output: Error: Missing file for output redirection

15. Mixed Cases
    - Input: echo "Hello" > file.txt | grep "Hello" >> output.txt &
    - Output: Pipes: [("echo", ["Hello"]), ("grep", ["Hello"])]
    - Output Redirection: file.txt
    - Append Output: output.txt
    - Background: true
